WEBVTT

00:24.440 --> 00:25.190
Your Highness,

00:25.190 --> 00:26.960
Armory Director, Yang Yi,
has committed suicide by poison.

00:26.960 --> 00:28.160
These 3 registrars are

00:28.160 --> 00:29.800
all in charge of purchasing
the repeating crossbows.

00:29.800 --> 00:32.030
-My Lord! We realize our mistake!
-We know our mistake!

00:32.030 --> 00:33.520
My Lord, don't kill us!

00:33.520 --> 00:34.470
Don't kill us!

00:34.470 --> 00:35.600
Spare our lives!

00:35.600 --> 00:37.280
We really don't know anything!

00:35.710 --> 00:38.540
[Heir of Prince Jing'an, Xiao Sheng;
courtesy name: Wuyi]

00:37.470 --> 00:38.960
My Lord, don't kill us!

00:38.960 --> 00:40.560
Spare us, My Lord!

00:41.200 --> 00:41.710
My Lord.

00:43.320 --> 00:45.280
It was the Armory Director
who took bribes from others.

00:45.280 --> 00:46.640
We know nothing.

00:46.790 --> 00:48.600
-Yes!
-Spare us, My Lord!

00:50.920 --> 00:52.350
Spare us, My Lord!

00:52.970 --> 00:54.100
Give me a name.

00:56.350 --> 00:57.710
I really don't know!

00:59.000 --> 01:01.600
It was all done
by the Armory Director, Yang Yi!

01:09.120 --> 01:09.680
My Lord!

01:10.430 --> 01:11.400
My Lord, don't kill me!

01:11.400 --> 01:12.530
You are quite lucky.

01:14.370 --> 01:15.370
Still won't talk?

01:15.370 --> 01:17.120
It's... It's Prince Changsha!

01:18.280 --> 01:19.039
Very good.

01:19.039 --> 01:19.760
My Lord.

01:21.120 --> 01:22.320
Please don't kill me!

01:26.789 --> 01:28.050
My Lord, don't kill me!

03:02.830 --> 03:08.080
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

03:08.730 --> 03:11.060
[Episode 1]

03:11.670 --> 03:14.190
Your Highness, the Valiant Cavalry
has been completely wiped out.

03:14.190 --> 03:15.600
The Northern Qin's Army is pressing
on the border.

03:15.600 --> 03:16.840
The Eagle King has started
to attack the city!

03:16.840 --> 03:17.900
Change into armor!

03:28.280 --> 03:29.120
Zhang Ji, Feng Wu!

03:29.120 --> 03:30.400
-Yes, Your Highness!
-Yes, Your Highness!

03:30.400 --> 03:31.590
You two lead the death squad

03:31.590 --> 03:33.120
to secretly put fish oil,
dry wood, and sulfur

03:33.120 --> 03:34.800
in the granaries and armories.

03:34.800 --> 03:36.240
Once the enemy breaks into the city,

03:36.240 --> 03:38.030
seal the gates
and reduce everything to ashes.

03:38.030 --> 03:39.829
Burn the entire Jiuzhang Plain.

03:39.840 --> 03:41.280
Please think twice, Your Highness.

03:41.280 --> 03:42.430
You are the Beifu Commander.

03:41.530 --> 03:42.790
[Zhang Ji,
Lieutenant General of Beifu Army]

03:42.680 --> 03:43.590
If anything happens to you...

03:43.590 --> 03:44.790
If I don't act as bait,

03:45.970 --> 03:47.870
how can we lure the Eagle King's army
into the city?

03:47.870 --> 03:50.270
How else can we avenge
the Valiant Cavalry?

03:51.310 --> 03:52.710
Where are the Beifu soldiers?

03:52.710 --> 03:53.560
-Here!
-Here!

03:54.880 --> 03:55.810
Raise your wine.

03:56.030 --> 03:56.910
-Yes!
-Yes!

03:58.190 --> 03:59.990
We are outnumbered by our enemy!

04:00.190 --> 04:02.120
Will you fight to the death with me?

04:02.150 --> 04:03.210
-We will!
-We will!

04:03.960 --> 04:05.420
If we can't make it back...

04:05.960 --> 04:07.560
-Then so be it!
-Then so be it!

04:08.630 --> 04:09.960
Who says we stand alone?

04:10.000 --> 04:11.200
We share weal and woe.

04:11.480 --> 04:12.680
Holding onto our brotherhood,

04:12.680 --> 04:14.480
we face life and death together!

04:14.560 --> 04:15.890
It will be proven today.

04:18.970 --> 04:19.579
Fight!

04:20.040 --> 04:22.600
-Fight! Fight! Fight!
-Fight! Fight! Fight!

04:32.210 --> 04:34.330
[Jiuzhang Plain, Ye]

04:41.830 --> 04:52.040
-Charge!
-Charge!

05:14.800 --> 05:19.080
♪ Fight and let flames
sweep the plains in darkness ♪

05:19.360 --> 05:22.540
♪ Still hot-blooded ♪

05:23.090 --> 05:25.890
♪ Our original intention won't change ♪

05:25.960 --> 05:30.540
♪ Fight to the bitter end ♪

05:30.580 --> 05:33.680
♪ My promises endure like a river ♪

05:34.400 --> 05:37.320
♪ I dare you to challenge me ♪

05:37.560 --> 05:40.350
♪ Listen, the winds begin to roar ♪

05:40.490 --> 05:43.170
♪ The clash of arms rages on ♪

05:43.320 --> 05:45.140
♪ Let flames
sweep the plains in darkness ♪

05:45.159 --> 05:48.110
♪ Still hot-blooded ♪

05:48.680 --> 05:52.720
♪ Fight and let flames
sweep the plains in darkness ♪

05:53.340 --> 05:58.470
♪ My promises endure like a river ♪

05:59.180 --> 06:03.530
♪ I dare you ♪

07:06.600 --> 07:08.750
Urgent military report
from Jiuzhang Plain!

07:08.750 --> 07:11.280
Urgent military report
from Jiuzhang Plain!

07:14.430 --> 07:16.080
[Jiankang, Ye]

07:16.380 --> 07:18.220
[Grand Tutor's Mansion]

07:23.040 --> 07:23.750
Mrs. Bai,

07:23.170 --> 07:25.760
[Princess Yunzhao, Li Fuhua]
[Mrs. Bai] [Mr. Bai]

07:24.430 --> 07:26.440
Jiayu always sits in on classes
at the Imperial Academy.

07:26.440 --> 07:28.970
She is quiet, gentle,
graceful, and refined.

07:29.630 --> 07:31.870
Your Highness,
is this what you meant by "quiet, gentle,

07:31.870 --> 07:33.270
graceful, and refined"?

07:33.430 --> 07:34.750
Lin, let's go.

07:35.040 --> 07:37.100
-Let's go.
-Mrs. Bai, please hold on.

07:40.980 --> 07:42.840
[Xie Jiayu, Grand Tutor Xie's daughter]

07:46.390 --> 07:47.120
Mrs. Bai,

07:47.360 --> 07:48.120
Mr. Bai,

07:48.230 --> 07:50.590
I'd like to greet you.

07:52.040 --> 07:52.640
It's okay.

07:54.750 --> 07:55.870
I've long heard

07:55.870 --> 07:58.560
about Mr. Bai's handsome looks and talent.

07:59.510 --> 08:00.560
Seeing you today,

08:00.750 --> 08:02.280
I realize it's indeed true.

08:06.160 --> 08:07.550
What's wrong, Mr. Bai?

08:07.830 --> 08:08.950
You look so pale.

08:09.630 --> 08:10.960
Are you feeling unwell?

08:12.070 --> 08:14.040
-Lin!
-Young Master! Young Master!

08:14.040 --> 08:16.600
Lin! Lin! Lin!

08:19.800 --> 08:20.390
Lin?

08:29.530 --> 08:30.790
Who bought the konjac?

08:34.159 --> 08:35.549
It was planted in the backyard.

08:35.549 --> 08:36.750
What about the fish maw?

08:36.750 --> 08:38.240
It's what you left over
last night, Mother.

08:38.240 --> 08:39.200
And what about the blood?

08:39.200 --> 08:40.929
I used chicken blood to fake it.

08:41.130 --> 08:43.460
So it doesn't look quite like human blood.

08:43.549 --> 08:44.550
It's a bit darker.

08:44.830 --> 08:47.120
Pig blood should work better next time.

08:48.870 --> 08:50.630
And this creepy hair?

08:50.630 --> 08:52.080
Mother, that's not hair.

08:52.080 --> 08:54.410
It's from the tails of Lightning and Dilu.

08:54.660 --> 08:56.570
I only cut off this tiny bit.

08:56.870 --> 08:58.480
They are steeds bestowed by His Majesty!

08:58.480 --> 09:00.270
Don't worry, Mother. It will grow back.

09:00.270 --> 09:00.870
Cang'er!

09:01.480 --> 09:02.340
You not only let

09:02.600 --> 09:03.870
the Young Lady mess around,

09:03.870 --> 09:05.390
but also kept watch for her.

09:05.390 --> 09:07.060
[Cang'er]

09:06.600 --> 09:07.200
Guards!

09:07.670 --> 09:09.130
Hold her down and beat her!

09:10.160 --> 09:11.560
Today, I will let you know

09:11.670 --> 09:13.150
what it means
to turn a fake act into reality.

09:13.150 --> 09:15.030
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

09:15.030 --> 09:16.600
Mother, just beat me
if you want to beat someone.

09:16.600 --> 09:18.130
Don't involve others in it.

09:19.600 --> 09:21.120
But I've already told you, Mother,

09:21.120 --> 09:22.120
I only want Mao.

09:24.030 --> 09:25.840
Since you won't listen to me, Mother,

09:25.840 --> 09:27.480
I won't listen to you, either.

09:27.480 --> 09:28.610
That should be fair.

09:28.790 --> 09:29.750
Marriage is

09:30.150 --> 09:31.240
determined by parents.

09:31.240 --> 09:32.970
How can you decide it yourself?

09:33.910 --> 09:34.630
Beat her!

09:43.210 --> 09:44.710
[Nanxing]

10:09.910 --> 10:11.840
Is this really Xiao Wuyi's coffin?

10:12.030 --> 10:14.360
No way. How could a figure
like Young Lord Xiao

10:14.360 --> 10:15.690
die in battle so easily?

10:16.000 --> 10:17.510
No matter how good
Xiao Wuyi is at fighting,

10:17.510 --> 10:18.320
he is still human.

10:17.790 --> 10:19.760
[Xie Huaigui, Grand Tutor of Southern Ye]

10:18.750 --> 10:19.870
Look at this coffin.

10:19.870 --> 10:21.840
It's a specification
that only a prince can use.

10:21.840 --> 10:24.120
If it's not Xiao Wuyi,
who else could it be?

10:24.120 --> 10:26.080
But how could Jiuzhang Plain
be seized by others?

10:26.080 --> 10:28.480
All because Xiao Wuyi thought
he was smart.

10:28.910 --> 10:31.170
Do you know any inside information, bro?

10:32.390 --> 10:35.320
-Greetings, Grand Tutor.
-Greetings, Grand Tutor.

10:36.000 --> 10:37.790
Speak and act cautiously.

10:38.600 --> 10:40.790
Do not discuss state affairs.

10:41.270 --> 10:41.930
-Yes.
-Yes.

10:46.120 --> 10:48.080
Master, please save Lady Jiayu.

10:48.510 --> 10:51.110
If you don't go back,
her life will be in danger!

10:52.510 --> 10:53.840
Okay, hurry.

10:58.440 --> 10:59.480
Stop, stop.

10:59.580 --> 11:00.820
Go, go away.

11:02.630 --> 11:03.630
It must have hurt so much!

11:03.630 --> 11:04.270
Father,

11:04.910 --> 11:06.150
you are finally back.

11:07.200 --> 11:09.330
Darling, no matter how angry you were,

11:09.590 --> 11:11.240
you shouldn't have beaten her like this.

11:11.240 --> 11:13.790
After all, Yao Yao is a girl.

11:15.000 --> 11:15.670
Father...

11:18.360 --> 11:19.420
Your good daughter

11:19.750 --> 11:22.280
trimmed the tails
of your two beloved horses.

11:24.630 --> 11:25.550
My... My...

11:25.870 --> 11:26.710
M-My...

11:27.870 --> 11:28.670
Dilu?

11:30.670 --> 11:31.480
Father.

11:33.150 --> 11:33.720
It hurts.

11:35.000 --> 11:35.930
It really hurts.

11:36.960 --> 11:38.280
Isn't it just a horse?

11:38.870 --> 11:39.980
You still shouldn't have beaten her.

11:39.980 --> 11:42.380
When has she ever
taken a beating honestly?

11:48.150 --> 11:49.550
Why didn't you tie the cushion today?

11:49.550 --> 11:50.750
She didn't tie the cushion?

11:50.750 --> 11:52.950
Nanxing, fetch the physician quickly!

11:53.030 --> 11:53.690
Yes, Madam.

11:54.740 --> 11:56.720
Are you trying to infuriate me to death?

11:56.720 --> 11:57.920
Since you didn't tie the cushion,

11:57.920 --> 12:00.320
why didn't you cry out
when you were beaten?

12:00.550 --> 12:02.670
You don't care about me anyway, Mother.

12:02.670 --> 12:04.270
So crying out was pointless.

12:05.270 --> 12:08.000
If beating me could
make you feel better, Mother,

12:08.280 --> 12:09.190
I'd just let you beat me.

12:09.190 --> 12:10.190
I could endure it.

12:12.440 --> 12:13.270
Darling,

12:14.240 --> 12:15.700
Yao Yao knows she is wrong.

12:16.120 --> 12:17.980
She won't dare to do it ever again.

12:20.230 --> 12:21.430
You always spoil her.

12:21.910 --> 12:23.640
That's why she is so unruly now.

12:24.180 --> 12:27.380
I'm anxious to arrange a marriage for her
just because...

12:28.750 --> 12:29.350
Forget it.

12:29.760 --> 12:31.320
I can't discipline you anymore.

12:31.320 --> 12:33.380
Let the Xies' ancestors educate you.

12:33.630 --> 12:34.790
Go reflect on your mistakes
at the ancestral hall.

12:34.790 --> 12:36.150
Copy the "Book of Rites" 100 times.

12:36.150 --> 12:38.810
You are not allowed to come out
until you finish.

12:38.870 --> 12:40.390
Yes, copy.

12:42.320 --> 12:43.790
Mother, I will do it.

12:44.200 --> 12:45.510
I will copy it 100 times.

12:45.510 --> 12:46.370
Your Highness,

12:46.440 --> 12:47.840
Prince Changsha is here.

12:48.320 --> 12:49.320
Prince Changsha?

12:50.390 --> 12:51.840
Stay put here and behave yourself.

12:51.840 --> 12:52.700
Don't come out.

12:58.840 --> 13:00.720
Your Highness, what are these?

13:02.440 --> 13:04.680
[Prince Changsha]

13:02.550 --> 13:03.980
Betrothal gifts, of course.

13:03.980 --> 13:05.980
I have admired Jiayu for a long time.

13:06.120 --> 13:08.750
So I specifically came
to deliver the betrothal gifts today.

13:08.750 --> 13:09.610
Where is Jiayu?

13:10.120 --> 13:10.910
Jiayu!

13:11.270 --> 13:12.320
-Jiayu?
-Your...

13:12.360 --> 13:13.720
Your Highness, you must be joking.

13:13.720 --> 13:15.030
Jiayu is still young.

13:15.670 --> 13:17.270
She is not in a hurry to get married.

13:17.270 --> 13:19.320
Why did I hear
that Her Highness has recently

13:19.320 --> 13:21.200
been looking
for a marriage match for Jiayu?

13:21.200 --> 13:21.910
But unfortunately,

13:21.910 --> 13:23.870
Jiayu didn't take a liking to any of them.

13:23.870 --> 13:25.440
She even scared away

13:26.150 --> 13:27.480
Young Master Bai today.

13:29.840 --> 13:30.510
So,

13:31.120 --> 13:32.630
Jiayu is still too young

13:32.960 --> 13:33.800
and immature.

13:34.550 --> 13:36.390
I plan to keep her by my side

13:37.080 --> 13:38.750
and discipline her for a few more years.

13:38.750 --> 13:40.210
That would be even better.

13:40.750 --> 13:43.120
Your Highness, you carry on
the late Empress Dowager's

13:43.120 --> 13:44.250
imperial demeanor.

13:44.480 --> 13:45.870
And the Grand Tutor, needless to say,

13:45.870 --> 13:47.670
boasts the elegance of a noble family.

13:47.670 --> 13:50.320
In the future,
when Jiayu follows me into the palace,

13:50.320 --> 13:52.850
she will surely impress the world
as empress.

13:53.030 --> 13:55.150
Your Highness, the Xie family and I

13:55.720 --> 13:58.980
have no intention
of sending Jiayu to the imperial palace.

14:14.150 --> 14:15.210
It doesn't matter.

14:15.270 --> 14:16.070
She is young,

14:16.670 --> 14:18.770
so you, my aunt, and the Grand Tutor
can't bear to let her go.

14:18.770 --> 14:19.730
I can wait.

14:20.390 --> 14:21.320
However, I

14:21.590 --> 14:24.360
also admire
the Grand Tutor's talent and dignity.

14:24.360 --> 14:25.630
In three days, at the Lantai gathering,

14:25.630 --> 14:27.700
I will hold a poetry gathering
at the Mid-Lake Pavilion.

14:27.700 --> 14:28.830
Grand Tutor, I'll be

14:29.750 --> 14:32.410
waiting for you
to give your guidance on poetry.

14:33.840 --> 14:34.440
Farewell.

14:39.790 --> 14:41.050
What an arrogant jerk.

14:41.440 --> 14:43.030
If the world falls into his hands,

14:43.030 --> 14:45.430
wouldn't the people be like
living in hell?

14:46.030 --> 14:48.360
Prince Changsha has been forming factions,

14:48.360 --> 14:50.560
craving the support of noble families.

14:51.120 --> 14:53.750
If it weren't to win over you
and the honest officials,

14:53.750 --> 14:55.950
he wouldn't have targeted Jiayu at all.

14:56.200 --> 14:57.240
It's my fault.

14:59.230 --> 15:01.680
I don't allow you
to go to that poetry gathering.

15:01.680 --> 15:03.540
I didn't say I was going, Darling.

15:04.790 --> 15:07.670
You are in such a hurry
to arrange a marriage for Yao Yao,

15:07.670 --> 15:09.960
but she likes Mao.

15:10.270 --> 15:12.470
Prince Changsha is out of the question,

15:12.580 --> 15:14.180
and Prince Qi is even more so.

15:15.030 --> 15:17.120
In view of Prince Changsha's eagerness,

15:17.120 --> 15:18.960
I'm afraid it will happen soon.

15:25.670 --> 15:27.530
You've started copying already?

15:28.000 --> 15:28.550
Father.

15:29.320 --> 15:31.150
I brought you some food.

15:31.510 --> 15:32.570
Thank you, Father.

15:35.240 --> 15:37.270
I thought you were copying the book.

15:38.480 --> 15:40.150
What are you designing now?

15:43.360 --> 15:45.160
Father, lend me your jade crown.

15:46.600 --> 15:49.030
You're giving this jade crown to Mao?

15:52.240 --> 15:54.510
Mao left the capital on a mission
for the Empress Dowager this time.

15:54.510 --> 15:57.030
He went to Qingyun Mountain to seek
medical help and pray for His Majesty.

15:57.030 --> 15:59.490
It is said that he found
a miraculous doctor.

15:59.510 --> 16:01.960
Then the Empress Dowager
will definitely reward him.

16:01.960 --> 16:02.720
Mao said

16:03.000 --> 16:05.530
that when the time comes,
he will ask for a fief

16:06.440 --> 16:08.100
and then come to propose to me.

16:08.790 --> 16:11.200
This will be
the most important day of his life.

16:11.200 --> 16:12.860
I want to give him a jade crown,

16:13.000 --> 16:15.030
so he can look his best on that day.

16:18.030 --> 16:19.630
Why are you sighing, Father?

16:19.790 --> 16:21.360
I'm jealous.

16:21.480 --> 16:22.120
Jealous?

16:22.790 --> 16:24.670
I haven't even received

16:24.670 --> 16:27.080
a jade crown personally designed
by my daughter,

16:27.080 --> 16:29.200
but that boy beat me to it.

16:29.790 --> 16:30.600
Father!

16:30.840 --> 16:33.040
Mao is the student you're most proud of.

16:33.630 --> 16:34.840
If you like it, Father,

16:34.840 --> 16:36.200
when it's your birthday,

16:36.200 --> 16:39.150
I'll buy a piece of fine jade
and carve one for you myself.

16:39.150 --> 16:40.010
How about that?

16:41.200 --> 16:42.660
I don't need these things.

16:43.320 --> 16:45.670
I'll just be happy as long as you cause

16:46.390 --> 16:48.050
less trouble for your mother.

16:50.000 --> 16:51.870
Come on, eat it while it's hot.

16:51.870 --> 16:52.390
Okay.

17:01.120 --> 17:02.670
My Lady, please get off.

17:06.510 --> 17:07.680
My Lady,
I really don't think I can do this.

17:07.680 --> 17:08.510
Maybe I should just go back.

17:08.510 --> 17:09.790
You can do this. Come on.

17:09.790 --> 17:10.400
Trust yourself.

17:10.400 --> 17:11.530
-Let's go.
-I can't.

17:17.240 --> 17:19.569
You are Young Master of Miraculous Craft.

17:20.349 --> 17:21.160
Yes, it's me.

17:21.440 --> 17:22.750
I heard you two want to negotiate

17:22.750 --> 17:24.829
a big deal worth 3,000 taels of silver.

17:24.829 --> 17:26.000
What exactly do you want to buy?

17:26.000 --> 17:27.300
Young Master of Miraculous Craft,

17:27.300 --> 17:28.790
can you really make anything?

17:28.790 --> 17:29.640
Of course.

17:30.030 --> 17:31.480
From flying wooden kites

17:31.480 --> 17:32.720
to waterwheels for drawing water,

17:32.720 --> 17:34.510
as long as it's a mechanical device,

17:34.510 --> 17:35.710
there is nothing I...

17:37.480 --> 17:39.880
There's nothing our Young Lady can't make.

17:41.160 --> 17:42.640
Three feet long, weighing sixteen taels,

17:42.640 --> 17:43.680
portable,

17:43.680 --> 17:45.830
a repeating crossbow
that shoots four arrows at once.

17:45.830 --> 17:46.690
Can you make it?

17:57.160 --> 17:57.720
What?

17:58.590 --> 17:59.520
Are you stumped?

18:01.240 --> 18:02.400
What do you need

18:03.200 --> 18:04.110
this item for, sir?

18:04.110 --> 18:05.110
It's a gift.

18:05.640 --> 18:06.790
It's a weapon of slaughter.

18:06.790 --> 18:08.070
Who would dare to receive such a gift?

18:08.070 --> 18:09.330
Why do you care so much?

18:09.510 --> 18:11.170
Just tell me if you can make it.

18:13.790 --> 18:14.350
I can't.

18:14.440 --> 18:15.240
You're lying!

18:17.000 --> 18:18.960
My younger brother
likes to hunt wild bears.

18:18.960 --> 18:21.110
We heard that you can make
a four-shot repeating crossbow,

18:21.110 --> 18:22.310
so we came here for it.

18:22.310 --> 18:25.510
Three thousand taels of silver.
The price is negotiable.

18:29.700 --> 18:30.980
If you like hunting,

18:31.400 --> 18:34.530
Young Master of Miraculous Craft
has other mechanisms.

18:37.310 --> 18:39.480
This Whistling Arrow
can drive away wolves at night.

18:39.480 --> 18:40.560
And these Nine-Linked Rings

18:40.560 --> 18:41.640
can be used either as a trap

18:41.640 --> 18:42.400
or as a lock.

18:43.000 --> 18:43.750
This Breezing Powder...

18:43.750 --> 18:44.350
Enough.

18:45.200 --> 18:46.440
I don't want any of these.

18:46.440 --> 18:48.440
I just want the repeating crossbow.

18:55.550 --> 18:57.480
I can make it, but I won't.

18:58.310 --> 18:58.920
Why?

18:59.510 --> 19:01.110
This three-feet,
four-arrow repeating crossbow

19:01.110 --> 19:02.710
was custom-made for a buyer.

19:03.240 --> 19:05.770
It was agreed
that it could only be sold to him.

19:06.400 --> 19:08.600
Being merchants, we must keep our word.

19:09.000 --> 19:10.640
No matter how much you pay me,

19:11.360 --> 19:12.270
Young Master

19:13.000 --> 19:15.660
of Miraculous Craft
still won't take this deal.

19:16.680 --> 19:18.270
You are
the real Young Master of Miraculous Craft.

19:18.270 --> 19:20.240
Tell me who that buyer is.

19:25.750 --> 19:26.680
Will you let us go

19:27.070 --> 19:28.000
if I tell you?

19:28.590 --> 19:30.520
If you tell me, you'll suffer less.

19:30.590 --> 19:32.520
Creating such a harmful thing, you

19:32.680 --> 19:33.400
deserve to die.

19:33.400 --> 19:34.200
Fine.

19:34.750 --> 19:36.210
Don't you just want a name?

19:36.310 --> 19:37.200
I'll tell you.

19:37.550 --> 19:38.070
Say it!

19:39.160 --> 19:40.920
He said his surname is

19:41.720 --> 19:42.240
Xiao.

19:42.960 --> 19:43.550
Xiao?

19:45.590 --> 19:46.590
And his given name is Sheng.

19:46.590 --> 19:47.200
What?

19:48.400 --> 19:49.200
Xiao Sheng?

20:12.000 --> 20:12.510
Jump!

20:12.880 --> 20:13.610
I don't dare.

20:15.110 --> 20:15.770
Stop there!

20:16.680 --> 20:17.480
It's too late.

20:31.920 --> 20:33.160
Toys!

20:33.680 --> 20:34.810
Come and take a look!

20:37.400 --> 20:39.110
Fortunately, I was prepared,

20:39.400 --> 20:41.440
and asked you to switch carriages
to pick me up.

20:40.060 --> 20:41.700
[Li Lejun, Princess Pingning]

20:42.070 --> 20:43.200
You knew it was a trap.

20:43.200 --> 20:44.680
Why did you still take the risk?

20:44.680 --> 20:46.410
I was just trying to make money.

20:46.440 --> 20:47.880
The monthly allowance my mother gives me

20:47.880 --> 20:50.440
is nowhere near enough
to make a jade crown for Mao.

20:50.440 --> 20:52.570
It's just a pity to lose such a big deal.

20:52.830 --> 20:55.630
As expected,
there's no such thing as a free lunch.

20:56.640 --> 20:57.790
I just don't know

20:57.790 --> 20:59.510
who Xiao Sheng is.

20:59.720 --> 21:01.350
What kind of trouble did he stir up

21:01.350 --> 21:04.160
to bring people to me,
Young Master of Miraculous Craft?

21:04.160 --> 21:06.310
I hope he didn't shoot anyone.

21:07.270 --> 21:08.790
You don't know who he is,

21:09.110 --> 21:10.350
yet you dared to sell it?

21:10.350 --> 21:11.830
He had money, and I had the goods.

21:11.830 --> 21:13.630
Why should I care about who he is?

21:14.960 --> 21:15.560
By the way.

21:17.720 --> 21:19.440
It's the letter my brother wrote to you.

21:19.440 --> 21:21.500
When is Mao returning to the capital?

21:31.590 --> 21:32.190
You say it.

21:37.070 --> 21:38.680
We underestimated the enemy.

21:38.680 --> 21:41.240
We didn't expect Young Master
of Miraculous Craft to be a woman.

21:41.240 --> 21:43.100
She threw some weird gadgets at us

21:43.240 --> 21:44.030
and got away.

21:45.050 --> 21:49.110
She also said the one who bought
the repeating crossbows i-is Xiao Sheng.

22:08.400 --> 22:09.310
Xiao Sheng?

22:10.400 --> 22:11.200
Me?

22:13.000 --> 22:13.790
It must've been Prince Changsha

22:13.790 --> 22:16.450
intentionally using your name,
Your Highness.

22:19.640 --> 22:20.720
Rest assured, Your Highness.

22:20.720 --> 22:21.920
No matter what it costs,

22:21.920 --> 22:23.310
I will find this woman

22:23.720 --> 22:26.590
and get solid proof
of her collusion with Prince Changsha.

22:26.590 --> 22:27.720
But I feel like

22:28.070 --> 22:29.350
she doesn't seem to be in cahoots

22:29.350 --> 22:30.610
with Prince Changsha.

22:30.790 --> 22:32.150
Do you have any evidence?

22:32.150 --> 22:33.280
It's just a feeling.

22:36.030 --> 22:38.290
Your Highness, this is what she dropped.

22:39.480 --> 22:41.410
This is an official tribute satin.

22:42.240 --> 22:44.840
It's specifically made
by the imperial court.

22:45.200 --> 22:48.270
Only the female relatives
of noble families can have it.

22:48.270 --> 22:49.720
Is there a record
in the Household Department's archives?

22:49.720 --> 22:50.780
So what if there is?

22:51.030 --> 22:52.400
With so many noble female relatives,

22:52.400 --> 22:54.460
are we supposed to ask them one by one?

22:54.790 --> 22:56.400
How's the investigation
on Prince Changsha?

22:56.400 --> 22:57.640
As our spies reported last night,

22:57.640 --> 22:59.640
Prince Changsha will hold
a poetry gathering at the Lantai gathering.

22:59.640 --> 23:01.030
He's invited lots of officials,

23:01.030 --> 23:02.960
claiming it's to review the world's poems.

23:02.960 --> 23:04.750
But he just wants to use the chance
to win over the officials.

23:04.750 --> 23:07.680
He really thought you died in battle,
Your Highness.

23:07.830 --> 23:08.890
Lantai gathering?

23:09.880 --> 23:11.350
This is a great opportunity
for the young masters and ladies

23:11.350 --> 23:13.070
of noble families to size each other up.

23:13.070 --> 23:15.960
Maybe Young Master of Miraculous Craft
will attend it, too.

23:15.960 --> 23:17.480
We can just go join the fun.

23:21.720 --> 23:24.000
By the way,
is there any news from Yongzhou?

23:24.000 --> 23:26.590
Have you found
Armory Director Yang Yi's family?

23:26.590 --> 23:27.270
Not yet.

23:31.790 --> 23:33.240
I think he will definitely like

23:33.240 --> 23:34.840
everything designed by you.

23:35.830 --> 23:38.630
That's true.
I've spent a lot of time designing it.

23:39.920 --> 23:40.830
Greetings, Your Highness.

23:40.830 --> 23:41.410
Mother.

23:41.590 --> 23:43.390
No need for formalities, Lejun.

23:44.480 --> 23:45.720
Where have you been all day?

23:45.720 --> 23:48.720
I went to Prince Qi's Mansion
to find Lejun, of course.

23:48.720 --> 23:49.400
And I

23:49.400 --> 23:51.500
spent the whole day
copying the "Book of Rites."

23:51.500 --> 23:52.630
My hands are so sore.

23:52.680 --> 23:53.350
Really?

23:54.200 --> 23:55.000
Today...

23:56.880 --> 23:59.440
Jiayu was with me.

24:01.170 --> 24:03.900
Your injuries haven't healed.
Don't run around.

24:04.350 --> 24:06.310
Once you're healed,
go kneel in the ancestral hall.

24:06.310 --> 24:07.360
Mother, I...

24:07.390 --> 24:09.050
Don't think you can escape it.

24:12.110 --> 24:12.700
Mother,

24:13.070 --> 24:14.750
can you take me
to attend the Lantai gathering

24:14.750 --> 24:16.080
the day after tomorrow?

24:16.590 --> 24:17.990
When did I say I was going?

24:18.430 --> 24:19.690
Don't you want to enjoy

24:19.880 --> 24:21.480
that beautiful scenery, Mother?

24:21.480 --> 24:22.870
What are you plotting now?

24:22.870 --> 24:24.720
Mother, you got me wrong.

24:25.510 --> 24:27.480
I just want to apologize to Mr. Bai.

24:27.720 --> 24:29.680
After all, I was the one
acting improperly that day.

24:29.680 --> 24:31.030
Whether the matchmaking worked or not,

24:31.030 --> 24:32.590
we shouldn't lose our manners.

24:32.590 --> 24:34.310
You can go to the Lantai gathering,

24:34.310 --> 24:35.570
but no running around.

24:35.590 --> 24:36.830
Apologize sincerely.

24:36.830 --> 24:37.810
Don't worry, Mother.

24:37.810 --> 24:39.870
I promise I'll stick to you like glue.

24:41.190 --> 24:43.490
[Lantai gathering]

24:42.720 --> 24:44.180
Let's go take a look ahead.

24:45.960 --> 24:48.880
Mr. Bai, I offended you last time.

24:48.970 --> 24:51.290
Today, I'd like to apologize to you.

24:53.800 --> 24:55.400
Don't worry about it, Jiayu.

24:55.590 --> 24:57.390
I also misunderstood last time.

24:58.790 --> 24:59.790
This is my cousin.

25:01.030 --> 25:01.960
Nice to meet you.

25:02.550 --> 25:04.010
Nice to meet you, Miss Xie.

25:04.110 --> 25:05.640
Talk nicely with Mr. Bai.

25:05.750 --> 25:07.160
Remember not to run around.

25:07.160 --> 25:10.200
Do not go to the poetry gathering
at the Mid-Lake Pavilion, whatever you do.

25:10.200 --> 25:11.270
Please rest assured, Mother.

25:11.270 --> 25:12.350
I'm not interested in

25:12.350 --> 25:13.270
those poetry gatherings.

25:13.270 --> 25:15.330
I wouldn't go even if they invited me.

25:15.560 --> 25:16.930
Come and take a look.

25:17.000 --> 25:18.880
Absolutely top-quality items.

25:23.340 --> 25:25.030
Your fan is so beautiful.

25:25.440 --> 25:26.830
May I take a closer look?

25:27.470 --> 25:29.560
My cousin bought me this bamboo fan.

25:30.400 --> 25:32.260
It even has his inscription on it.

25:32.280 --> 25:33.940
It's the only one in the world.

25:34.240 --> 25:36.440
Mr. Bai's handwriting is really amazing.

25:36.440 --> 25:37.720
If you want one, Jiayu,

25:38.240 --> 25:40.070
I'll write an inscription for you.

25:40.070 --> 25:40.870
That's great!

25:41.590 --> 25:43.920
But I don't want an inscription on a fan.

25:44.900 --> 25:46.630
I want it on that celadon piece.

25:50.240 --> 25:50.970
Here you are.

25:57.290 --> 25:59.310
"The peach blossoms are in full bloom,

25:59.310 --> 26:00.170
brilliant..."

26:00.480 --> 26:02.640
Mr. Bai, you are truly amazing.

26:03.960 --> 26:05.370
Miss, I'll take this celadon.

26:05.370 --> 26:05.960
How much is it?

26:05.960 --> 26:06.920
100 taels of silver.

26:06.920 --> 26:09.070
100 taels of silver? Are you kidding me?

26:09.070 --> 26:10.850
This is made from the clay of Mount Xi,

26:10.850 --> 26:13.240
not to mention
this gentleman's inscription.

26:13.240 --> 26:14.550
It's unique in the world.

26:14.550 --> 26:15.750
No matter how great the inscription is,

26:15.750 --> 26:17.070
it's not worth this price.

26:17.070 --> 26:18.830
Even Prince Qi's poems aren't worth 100.

26:18.830 --> 26:20.160
I don't want it anymore.

26:20.400 --> 26:21.330
What do you mean?

26:21.590 --> 26:23.790
My cousin's poems are inferior
to Prince Qi's?

26:23.790 --> 26:24.310
Cousin.

26:26.200 --> 26:28.030
I mean, this seller is greedy.

26:28.720 --> 26:29.680
If I want it,

26:29.680 --> 26:30.510
I'll just ask Mr. Bai

26:30.510 --> 26:32.000
to write another one for me later.

26:32.000 --> 26:33.200
Why waste money on it?

26:33.270 --> 26:33.880
Stingy.

26:34.070 --> 26:35.790
Miss, I'll buy this celadon.

26:36.240 --> 26:36.750
Okay.

26:37.960 --> 26:38.510
Hold on.

26:39.880 --> 26:40.790
You are right.

26:41.120 --> 26:42.690
I'm here to apologize today.

26:42.690 --> 26:45.450
I'll just force myself
to buy this celadon.

26:45.880 --> 26:47.240
I already said I'd buy it.

26:47.240 --> 26:48.310
I'll add another 50 taels of silver.

26:48.310 --> 26:49.000
Two hundred taels.

26:49.000 --> 26:49.860
Two hundred...

26:50.870 --> 26:51.780
and one taels.

26:54.460 --> 26:55.320
Cousin, you...

26:56.790 --> 26:59.310
This celadon is mine now.

27:03.000 --> 27:04.550
There are really so many rich people.

27:04.250 --> 27:05.350
[The peach blossoms are
in full bloom, brilliant]

27:05.400 --> 27:06.160
Mr. Bai,

27:06.370 --> 27:07.720
I'm afraid I'm meant to miss out

27:07.720 --> 27:09.180
on your fine handwriting.

27:12.200 --> 27:13.060
I want this pot.

27:14.070 --> 27:14.640
Okay.

27:17.480 --> 27:19.080
Nine-Turn Mind-Changing Pot!

27:19.080 --> 27:20.030
Jiayu, where are you going?

27:20.030 --> 27:22.560
Cousin,
just leave that stingy person alone.

27:23.000 --> 27:25.500
Why is the Nine-Turn Mind-Changing Pot
out for sale?

27:25.500 --> 27:26.310
Didn't you specifically

27:26.310 --> 27:28.350
pick all these goods yesterday, My Lady?

27:28.350 --> 27:29.030
Oh, no.

27:29.270 --> 27:30.670
I must have misplaced it.

27:31.070 --> 27:32.790
Did you tell her
how to poison with this pot?

27:32.790 --> 27:34.450
I explained how to use it once.

27:34.640 --> 27:36.500
Turn left for poison and right for wine.

27:36.500 --> 27:38.200
She still bought it,
knowing how to use the poison?

27:38.200 --> 27:39.920
This person must be up to no good.

27:39.920 --> 27:41.250
I'll follow her and see.

27:42.720 --> 27:44.580
My Lady! Please don't run around!

27:46.410 --> 27:48.000
Move out of the way! Move!

27:50.070 --> 27:50.830
Move!

27:51.590 --> 27:52.110
Go away!

27:52.880 --> 27:53.410
Make way!

27:53.920 --> 27:55.320
Prince Changsha is here!

27:56.130 --> 27:56.830
Move!

27:58.650 --> 27:59.720
Prince Changsha?

28:00.400 --> 28:02.480
He's here for the poetry gathering, too?

28:02.480 --> 28:03.680
Can he compose poems?

28:12.840 --> 28:13.400
Chan.

28:15.440 --> 28:16.570
I've made up my mind.

28:17.440 --> 28:18.270
I'll put an end

28:19.030 --> 28:20.230
to everything today.

28:21.480 --> 28:22.410
After the dance,

28:22.640 --> 28:24.680
I'll curry favor with Prince Changsha.

28:24.680 --> 28:27.140
Then I'll drink
this poisoned wine with him.

28:29.600 --> 28:30.230
Sister,

28:31.310 --> 28:33.270
I'll take full responsibility for this.

28:33.270 --> 28:35.000
It has nothing to do with anyone else.

28:35.000 --> 28:35.400
No,

28:36.160 --> 28:37.490
we either live together

28:37.550 --> 28:38.480
or die together.

28:44.400 --> 28:46.130
How moving your sisterhood is.

28:46.830 --> 28:48.690
You want to kill Prince Changsha?

28:49.160 --> 28:49.830
Who are you?

28:50.720 --> 28:51.550
You can't.

28:52.720 --> 28:53.920
You want to expose us?

28:55.830 --> 28:56.640
I mean,

28:59.480 --> 29:00.610
this pot won't work.

29:00.920 --> 29:02.480
Although it was made of purple clay,

29:02.480 --> 29:04.010
the kiln temperature wasn't high enough,

29:04.010 --> 29:05.070
causing the body to crack

29:05.070 --> 29:06.200
and have a poor seal.

29:06.720 --> 29:09.380
Now the pot's both sides
contain poisoned wine.

29:09.880 --> 29:10.960
If you drink it,

29:11.270 --> 29:12.240
you'll die, too.

29:13.440 --> 29:14.310
How do you know?

29:14.400 --> 29:16.550
Because I made this pot.

29:20.590 --> 29:21.750
Then we'll die together.

29:21.750 --> 29:23.280
Do you have to do it this way?

29:23.440 --> 29:24.240
Is it worth it?

29:26.550 --> 29:28.440
Prince Changsha is a brutal tyrant.

29:28.440 --> 29:30.960
Every day, there are sisters
who are tortured to death by him.

29:30.960 --> 29:33.110
If I can exchange my life

29:33.550 --> 29:35.410
for a way out for my sisters today,

29:36.400 --> 29:37.200
it's worth it.

29:38.500 --> 29:39.830
If you dare to expose it,

29:40.200 --> 29:41.330
I'll kill you first.

29:43.460 --> 29:45.410
Your Highness, the Grand Tutor is ill.

29:43.790 --> 29:45.890
[Wei Qianli, Household Department Adjutant]
[Capital Prefect]

29:45.450 --> 29:47.310
I'm afraid he can't make it today.

29:47.310 --> 29:49.110
He just refuses to show respect
to you, Your Highness.

29:48.490 --> 29:50.560
[Chen Guangtong, Military Advisor]

29:49.640 --> 29:52.030
He's a mere teacher.
How dare he put on airs?

29:52.030 --> 29:54.190
The Xie family is the head
of the noble clans.

29:54.190 --> 29:56.510
Although Grand Tutor Xie
holds no court position,

29:56.510 --> 29:57.920
during the late Emperor's reign,

29:57.920 --> 29:59.920
he once served at the center
of the imperial government.

29:59.920 --> 30:02.780
Now the court is full
of the Xie family's disciples.

30:02.830 --> 30:04.110
They seem to have no faction,

30:04.110 --> 30:05.750
but their roots actually run deep

30:05.750 --> 30:07.000
as the leader of the honest officials.

30:07.000 --> 30:08.720
We cannot underestimate them.

30:08.720 --> 30:09.380
Never mind.

30:10.440 --> 30:12.240
Today, we only talk about bliss,

30:12.440 --> 30:13.350
but not anything else.

30:13.350 --> 30:14.310
Congratulations,

30:14.310 --> 30:15.200
Your Highness.

30:15.550 --> 30:17.110
Now that Xiao Wuyi is gone,

30:17.140 --> 30:19.500
the Beifu Army is leaderless.

30:19.590 --> 30:21.570
I heard you are very good
at painting and calligraphy.

30:21.570 --> 30:23.500
Take a look at this painting for me.

30:25.480 --> 30:26.340
Your Highness,

30:26.960 --> 30:28.890
this painting is truly marvelous.

30:28.960 --> 30:30.270
With grand mountains

30:30.680 --> 30:31.830
and waters,

30:32.200 --> 30:34.160
it looks very authentic.

30:34.310 --> 30:34.960
Nice.

30:35.800 --> 30:37.440
Let's drink to our hearts' content today!

30:37.440 --> 30:38.300
Play the music.

30:43.030 --> 30:43.920
Go this way.

30:44.400 --> 30:45.240
Where is this?

30:46.920 --> 30:47.720
Don't worry.

30:47.970 --> 30:49.500
I'm absolutely a good person.

30:49.500 --> 30:51.070
After you leave the Lantai gathering,

30:51.070 --> 30:52.550
go to the blacksmith shop
in the east of the city

30:52.550 --> 30:53.920
and find a half-blind old woman.

30:53.920 --> 30:56.510
Tell her Young Master of Miraculous Craft
sent you.

30:56.510 --> 30:57.640
She is really capable.

30:57.640 --> 31:00.070
She can help you
change your identities and leave the city.

31:00.070 --> 31:00.480
Let's go.

31:00.480 --> 31:01.960
But if Prince Changsha finds out
about what you're doing,

31:01.960 --> 31:03.020
he won't let you go.

31:04.750 --> 31:06.950
Don't worry, he can't do anything to me.

31:07.720 --> 31:08.650
Hurry, let's go.

31:08.680 --> 31:10.210
Keep up. All of you, keep up.

31:14.240 --> 31:16.440
Wait, what are you doing? Who are you?

31:16.550 --> 31:17.110
Freeze!

31:19.790 --> 31:20.720
It's you.

31:21.880 --> 31:22.550
Let go of me!

31:22.570 --> 31:24.370
What are you two up to?

31:24.510 --> 31:26.440
Young Master of Miraculous Craft,

31:26.680 --> 31:28.440
I suppose you've been doing well.

31:28.440 --> 31:29.070
Who are you?

31:29.070 --> 31:29.730
Don't move!

31:30.350 --> 31:30.920
Tell me

31:31.720 --> 31:33.320
which family's lady you are.

31:33.350 --> 31:34.550
Why should I tell you?

31:35.920 --> 31:36.480
Fine.

31:37.310 --> 31:38.840
After I finish my business,

31:39.030 --> 31:41.630
I'll come back and take my time
to deal with you.

31:44.390 --> 31:46.250
You want to kill Prince Changsha,

31:46.350 --> 31:47.000
right?

31:51.350 --> 31:52.480
What a coincidence.

31:53.030 --> 31:55.490
I have also been annoyed with him
for a long time.

31:55.490 --> 31:57.480
Take them away. Leave no one behind.

31:57.480 --> 31:58.340
How do we leave?

32:05.400 --> 32:07.600
The Heir of Prince Jing'an has arrived!

32:08.880 --> 32:10.410
The Heir of Prince Jing'an?

32:11.000 --> 32:11.920
Isn't he dead?

32:12.080 --> 32:14.080
Nice...

32:19.160 --> 32:20.200
Isn't he dead?

32:25.110 --> 32:26.590
Aren't you dead?

32:27.030 --> 32:28.630
Were you exhilarated seeing

32:29.030 --> 32:30.430
my coffin enter the city?

32:31.790 --> 32:33.520
Did you really think I was dead?

32:35.240 --> 32:37.240
As wise and mighty as you are,
Your Highness,

32:37.240 --> 32:38.240
you wouldn't die.

32:40.310 --> 32:42.040
So, which jerk spread the rumor

32:42.240 --> 32:44.440
that I died in battle in Jiuzhang Plain?

32:44.550 --> 32:45.030
You?

32:45.030 --> 32:45.550
No?

32:45.960 --> 32:46.440
You?

32:47.510 --> 32:48.350
Or you?

32:51.110 --> 32:52.350
Your Highness, I just ran into

32:52.350 --> 32:54.080
some of your dancers on the way,

32:54.160 --> 32:56.030
who were scheming to poison you,

32:56.550 --> 32:58.150
so I brought them over to you.

32:59.920 --> 33:01.200
Thank you, Your Highness.

33:01.200 --> 33:01.880
Guards!

33:02.120 --> 33:04.310
But I like her temper.

33:05.110 --> 33:06.910
I wonder if you can give her to me.

33:07.160 --> 33:08.240
If you like her,

33:08.830 --> 33:09.890
just take her away.

33:10.750 --> 33:13.080
Since you're so generous, Your Highness,

33:13.200 --> 33:16.130
why not also let me attend
today's Lantai gathering?

33:19.480 --> 33:20.750
Why did it suddenly

33:21.310 --> 33:23.110
become so quiet upon my arrival?

33:23.660 --> 33:25.590
Isn't it a poetry gathering today?

33:26.350 --> 33:27.200
Dance!

33:28.410 --> 33:29.470
And compose poems.

33:37.720 --> 33:38.580
Adjutant Chen,

33:39.270 --> 33:41.640
you are famous for your poems
in the capital.

33:41.640 --> 33:43.100
Write one for me right now.

33:43.720 --> 33:45.920
Your Highness,
what kind of poem do you want?

33:45.920 --> 33:48.550
Compose a poem
praising the battle in Jiuzhang Plain,

33:48.550 --> 33:50.350
where the Beifu Army
reversed a losing battle

33:50.350 --> 33:52.350
and killed the enemies heroically.

33:53.510 --> 33:54.970
I'm sorry, Your Highness.

33:55.110 --> 33:56.270
I don't know how to write poems.

33:56.270 --> 33:57.400
I can't do it for you.

33:59.960 --> 34:01.890
-He killed the man!
-He killed him!

34:02.360 --> 34:03.480
Are you crazy, Young Lord Xiao?

34:03.480 --> 34:04.510
How dare you kill an imperial official?

34:04.510 --> 34:05.970
No one is allowed to leave.

34:09.280 --> 34:11.510
If you leave, how will you pay
for the deaths of the 30,000 soldiers

34:11.510 --> 34:12.440
of my Beifu Army?

34:13.480 --> 34:14.480
Prince Changsha,

34:15.150 --> 34:17.010
he didn't know how to write poems.

34:17.920 --> 34:19.250
Do you know how to write?

34:22.830 --> 34:24.760
I don't believe you dare to kill me.

34:39.760 --> 34:40.620
He actually...

34:41.070 --> 34:42.670
He actually killed someone.

34:45.510 --> 34:47.550
People die in every battle.

34:52.670 --> 34:53.320
Fine.

34:54.030 --> 34:55.560
After I finish my business,

34:55.630 --> 34:58.230
I'll come back and take my time
to deal with you.

35:00.480 --> 35:02.360
Will he kill me later, too?

35:02.760 --> 35:04.440
No, I have to run away quickly.

35:19.030 --> 35:21.280
Do none of you really know
how to write poems?

35:21.280 --> 35:22.110
I do!

35:23.550 --> 35:26.590
-Me, too!
-I can also write!

35:28.070 --> 35:29.730
Continue the music and dance!

35:34.710 --> 35:35.320
Guys,

35:36.760 --> 35:37.990
if this dance ends,

35:38.710 --> 35:40.170
while the poem is not done,

35:41.290 --> 35:42.590
I will continue.

35:42.590 --> 35:43.710
I've finished writing.

35:43.710 --> 35:45.360
I've finished writing, too!

35:45.360 --> 35:47.320
Me, too.

35:47.320 --> 35:49.520
-Me, too.
-I've also finished writing.

35:52.800 --> 35:53.360
Read it.

35:53.730 --> 35:54.800
Dedicated to Young Lord Xiao.

35:54.800 --> 35:55.840
Not to me.

35:56.190 --> 35:57.800
Read it to Prince Changsha.

35:58.590 --> 35:59.230
Cold frost flies...

35:59.230 --> 36:00.190
Read it loudly!

36:00.480 --> 36:02.340
Cold frost flies over 1,000 feet.

36:02.710 --> 36:04.770
Wuyi subdued tigers with his valour.

36:04.840 --> 36:06.900
The army was drenched in enemy blood,

36:07.400 --> 36:09.660
defending the country like a bright sun.

36:10.670 --> 36:12.400
What a flattering poem.

36:14.400 --> 36:16.110
I'll let it pass, just barely.

36:16.960 --> 36:18.420
Thank you, Your Highness.

36:20.000 --> 36:21.800
Write it down and compose a tune.

36:22.050 --> 36:23.710
Send it to Prince Changsha
as a gift later.

36:23.710 --> 36:25.170
Thank you, Your Highness.

36:25.550 --> 36:26.360
Next one.

36:26.800 --> 36:29.440
With armored horses and spears,
banners fluttered in the wind.

36:29.440 --> 36:31.920
Brave warriors shed blood
on the battlefield.

36:31.920 --> 36:34.440
The long wind brought rain
like the tears of thousands of soldiers.

36:34.440 --> 36:37.970
Loyal souls from Jiuzhang Plain
bowed towards their hometown.

36:56.230 --> 36:58.310
Jiankang is so sunny and warm.

37:01.030 --> 37:02.320
Even now, the blood

37:03.840 --> 37:05.030
is still warm.

37:09.190 --> 37:10.650
Your Highness, do you know

37:11.760 --> 37:14.020
how cold the blood was in Jiuzhang Plain?

37:15.320 --> 37:18.180
Do you know
that the 18 coffins that entered the city

37:18.920 --> 37:22.650
actually contained 18 generals
of my Beifu Army who died unjustly?

37:39.670 --> 37:41.280
Actually, I don't care

37:42.110 --> 37:44.170
how you fight here in Jiankang at all.

37:44.710 --> 37:46.910
I also don't care who sits on the throne,

37:47.320 --> 37:49.120
whether it's you or His Majesty.

37:52.320 --> 37:54.150
But you made me change my mind.

37:56.230 --> 37:57.320
From today on,

37:58.400 --> 38:01.200
you won't get anything you want,
Prince Changsha.

38:01.870 --> 38:04.420
I'll snatch the person you want to marry.

38:04.920 --> 38:05.980
And I will also take

38:07.800 --> 38:09.330
whatever you already have.

38:15.320 --> 38:17.010
I was wrong. I was out of my mind.

38:17.010 --> 38:18.270
Your Highness, you...

38:32.840 --> 38:34.970
Your Highness, you are a generous man.

38:35.280 --> 38:35.960
I

38:36.730 --> 38:39.010
will chant sutras
and pray for the fallen soldiers

38:39.010 --> 38:40.450
every day.

38:44.630 --> 38:46.230
You still haven't found her?

38:46.360 --> 38:47.960
Who on earth did she go to see?

38:49.030 --> 38:49.630
Mother!

38:50.840 --> 38:52.840
-Mother.
-Where on earth did you go?

38:53.030 --> 38:54.550
I've just been to the restroom.

38:54.550 --> 38:56.680
Get in the carriage now. Let's go home.

39:03.190 --> 39:05.050
Your Highness, it's anesthetic.

39:14.280 --> 39:15.920
Go investigate the background

39:15.920 --> 39:17.280
of all the stalls
at today's Lantai gathering.

39:17.280 --> 39:18.680
Any stalls with this mark

39:18.920 --> 39:21.380
belong
to Young Master of Miraculous Craft.

39:22.420 --> 39:25.150
I'd like to know
which family on earth she's from.

39:25.490 --> 39:27.510
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

39:28.280 --> 39:29.400
Mother,

39:28.450 --> 39:30.670
[Xiao Ziqi] [He Yuanji,
Crown Princess in Prince Jing'an's family]

39:29.960 --> 39:31.440
I am sleepy.

39:31.020 --> 39:33.380
[Xiao Yao, Prince Jing'an's eldest son;
courtesy name: Anming]

39:32.030 --> 39:33.290
He didn't even say anything

39:33.290 --> 39:35.250
and just sent a dozen coffins home.

39:35.140 --> 39:36.740
[Yao Yunzhi, Prince Jing'an's consort]

39:35.360 --> 39:36.190
Anmin.

39:38.400 --> 39:40.600
Your Highness, Young Lord Xiao is back.

39:41.360 --> 39:42.020
Where is he?

39:42.070 --> 39:43.150
His Highness took the dancers

39:43.150 --> 39:45.150
and Madam Rui back to Fuying Courtyard.

39:45.150 --> 39:46.960
He said he'd rest early
for the court tomorrow morning,

39:46.960 --> 39:49.620
and he'd greet you, Your Highness,
another day.

39:51.590 --> 39:53.080
Is this called resting early?

39:53.080 --> 39:54.680
He is clearly having a party!

40:39.230 --> 40:40.440
That hurts like crazy.

40:40.440 --> 40:42.440
Keep messing around,
and you'll never recover.

40:40.610 --> 40:42.730
[Ruisheng, maid
who serves the Heir of Prince Jing'an]

40:45.070 --> 40:46.270
But I have you, right?

40:47.280 --> 40:48.590
Even the best physician

40:48.590 --> 40:50.850
can't save a patient who seeks his death.

40:50.920 --> 40:52.710
You barely survived this time.

40:52.960 --> 40:54.550
You must rest for half a year.

40:54.550 --> 40:56.150
Don't get worked up or fight.

40:56.230 --> 40:57.630
Once the injury relapses,

40:57.630 --> 40:59.030
even gods can't save you.

41:00.230 --> 41:01.560
What I need to do can't be

41:01.800 --> 41:03.060
put off for half a year.

41:05.510 --> 41:06.840
What are you going to do?

41:14.590 --> 41:16.710
Young Lord Xiao, you've worked hard
defending the territory these years

41:16.710 --> 41:18.110
and earned numerous military merits.

41:18.110 --> 41:20.370
You deserve a nice reward and promotion.

41:20.760 --> 41:21.150
You...

41:21.150 --> 41:22.670
Thank you for your grace, Your Majesty.

41:22.670 --> 41:24.970
I wouldn't dare decline the rewards
for my soldiers.

41:24.970 --> 41:27.400
But for myself,
I seek neither promotion nor titles.

41:27.400 --> 41:28.800
I only ask for one person.

41:29.440 --> 41:30.590
Please grant me this marriage,
Your Majesty.

41:30.590 --> 41:31.920
I wish to marry

41:32.350 --> 41:34.190
Grand Tutor Xie's daughter
as my principal consort.
